Text: Cc Vince Are you available to attend our next Advisory Meeting on June Here is the draft agenda AGENDAdraftdoc Please let me know Kate Fang Wharton Risk Management and Decision Processes Center AGENDAdraftdoc

RE Agenda for Advisory Committee Meeting on Dec Vince thanks for getting back to me We understand Shirley called me back and talked to me already We look forward to seeing you in the future meetings Kate Original Message From mailto Sent Tuesday November PM To Cc Subject RE Agenda for Advisory Committee Meeting on Dec Kate Thanks for your message With all the turbulence going on in Enron its difficult for anybody to leave the office for an extended period of time We shall have to abstain this time and hope to join you in the future Vince Original Message From Fang Fang ENRON Sent Monday November PM To Shanbhogue Vasant Cc Kunreuther Howard Kleindorfer Paul Newman Tara Subject FW Agenda for Advisory Committee Meeting on Dec Dear Vince and Vasant Since you both wont be able to come for our Advisory Committee meeting on Dec can you send someone else to come Please let me know it is critical for us to have someone from your team to come As you can see from the attached RSVP list we have a quite good mix of people to come FYI I am attaching an agenda and possible issues for your review Look forward to hearing from you Kate Original Message From Shanbhogue Vasant mailto Sent Monday November PM To Fang Fang Subject RE Agenda for Advisory Committee Meeting on Dec Hi Kate unfortunately due to business circumstances I will not be able to attend the Advisory Committee meeting Please give my apologies to Paul and Howard Thanks Vasant Shanbhogue Vice President Research Enron Wholesale Services Invite RSVP FINAL Listxls File Invite RSVP FINAL Listxls AGENDAdoc File AGENDAdoc
